OL,4,CAfghanistan investigates ban on girls'
OL,5,Csinging
OL,6, The Afghan education ministry says it
OL,7, is investigating a recent statement
OL,8, from the director of education in the
OL,9, capital, Kabul, which banned girls
OL,10, older than 12 from singing in public.
OL,12,FThe ban was widely criticised on social
OL,13,Fmedia. Girls shared clips of themselves
OL,14,Fsinging using the hashtag #IAmMySong.
OL,16,FThe row comes amid concerns about
OL,17,Fconsequences of a possible peace deal
OL,18,Fwith the Taliban.
OL,20,FUnder the Taliban, girls were denied an
OL,21,Feducation and most music was banned.
